<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hollfeld</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass seine Diener und weitere Nürnberger den Verbrecher Jobst Peler zu Hollfeld gefangen haben, aber dort selbst gefangen worden sind, und bittet, den Betroffenen gegen Peler zu ihrem Recht zu verhelfen, ihn zu befragen und die gefangenen Nürnberger freizulassen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_516" id="257r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_516_r1l31">Den von Holuelt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_516_r1l32"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als etlıch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> den Jobs Peler der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_516_r1l33"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>rawb<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>ſchedlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> man ıſt bey eẅch ʒu fenknuſſ bracht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_516_r1l34">haben alſo haben vns <expan>dıeſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> getan wıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_516_r1l35">ſıe mıtſampt <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> Peler auch ʒu fenknuſſ <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_516_r1l36">beheft ſeyn . <expan>Bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>mane<ex>n</ex></expan> wır eẅr <expan>freẅntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> mıt fleıſʒ </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_517" id="257v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_517_r2l1">eẅr <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vnd hılff darcʒu ʒu tun / daʒ vns vnd den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_517_r2l2"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> rechtes ʒu <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> peler bey eẅch geſtatt vnd ge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_517_r2l3">holffen vnd des gerawm tag geſecʒt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> dıe dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_517_r2l4"><expan>erlange<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>muge<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd daʒ <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> peler / vmb eıns <expan>gemeine<ex>n</ex></expan> nucʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_517_r2l5">wıllen <expan>ernſtl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſucht</expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> / Vnd daʒ auch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_517_r2l6">dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıe bey eẅch <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd beheft ſeyn / ledıg ge </ab>
